| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5419 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: fbb1cfc0-1131-5f0f-bace-0f15936ad4a7"
